Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最討厭與最喜歡的距離中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往往是推理與懸疑的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個漂亮的山水花園中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然發生了詭異的殺人凶案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過于常人的名偵探柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏果然不愧是號稱業界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山家具的社長家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是院子就跟別人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看到有瀑布的院子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就讓人感覺心情平靜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你們都這麽喜歡這個院子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你們來到寒舍就算是值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想差不多就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你們看了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你快看那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布的水開始滿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿出來的水都淹到院子裏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初設計的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就設定了每到早晚八點跟下午四點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓瀑布的水流到院子的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是水流到院子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會把沙子的擺設打亂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的水勢不至于讓沙子弄亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分鍾後就會自動排出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是前一任社長設計的山水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看到後都評價不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到晚餐的時候我們再好好聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于車子你就不用去擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我會讓秘書幫您開過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽都讓您費心真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人有困難就應該互相幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 淩佳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好招呼他們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 我一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個設計還真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人哪會知道維持這些東西要花多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山木那個家夥設計的這個什麽山水根本就是花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些白沙被水沖出的紋路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過水看得好清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上如果映著月亮一定很浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個景致真的沒話說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長有不少客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就專門會挑滿月的時候到家裏來玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯水酒配上富士山跟滿月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太痛快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那是什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是柱子上面吊的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是取物竿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取物竿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什麽東西掉在院子裏的白沙上的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得用到這根取物竿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則不就把白沙那麽漂亮的紋路給破壞掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計的人還真是會想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲換了馬島社長之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院設計師一個月只會來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始排水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計的還真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流石庭的玄機（前篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位如果膩了就請到客廳去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經爲大家准備了飯前酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 你說你沒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當我三歲小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差500萬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 加上利息是700萬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好在這個月裏把錢湊齊了還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就開除你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽清楚了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這棟別墅真是夠壯觀的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請進屋去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位請這邊坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去拿點飲料過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以給我一瓶啤酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽白天就喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽關系嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淩佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是幹什麽的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們三位是馬島社長的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們不是什麽往來的客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是到了三本坡那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到汽油剛好用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長又剛好經過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這才和馬島社長認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧社長人很親切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還邀請我們到他府上來晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽平易近人的社長還真是不多見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只會陌生人面前擺出一副好臉色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會這個樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是紀念木山家具一號店成立的晚餐會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與會的應該都是我們自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系來 遠藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長既然邀請他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說吃飯的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多幾個人 也比較香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是社長秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋本政之先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于這位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則是關系企業木山室內家飾的社長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤社長以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭術高明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還曾經代表國家參賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是好久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在早就生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于我自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫木山智則是一個自由作家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就是寫非洲漫遊之旅的那個木山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 你認識他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經到很多國家旅行寫了不少書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是看過你寫的非洲漫遊之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麽樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話可以跟你要個簽名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這次要辦一個攝影展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是門票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你來賞光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要送我門票啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我這就幫你簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支鋼筆好像很舊的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是家父的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是有名的牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我就是舍不得丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會一直帶在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以請你的朋友一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我一定會去參觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟然跟木山家具也有淵源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我還真的不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家公司就是由我父親創建的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我父親死後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長才接了他的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去看過山水了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片白沙的紋路實在太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片白沙和瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我父親 趁著忙碌的空檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點一滴用心打造完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 智則哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是怎麽死掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 這樣問不禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是去年車禍死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很難預料的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有個地方看到的夜景很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證你們不會失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去吧 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話你們去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真要我選的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甯可坐在這裏喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爸爸就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是看看的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證你看了不會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏和東京不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星特別近好像真的要掉下來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿這麽多杯太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也可以試試啤酒以外的酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待會再爲您端過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先喝這個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你不要這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法要流出來了 這很浪費的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一碰到酒他就沒分寸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如從命了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行行 這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我最近要辦一個攝影展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不嫌棄的話就請去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出你這小子挺努力的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會抽空去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上個月的營收報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的數字應該不會讓我看不下去才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 我已經把晚餐准備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽就請各位去餐廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等了這麽久 終于可以吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們木山家具的生意能夠蒸蒸日上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個肉好好吃哦 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 好軟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 再喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你那麽喜歡那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是難得的緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把它便宜讓你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真愛開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你跟你爸爸好好商量之後再決定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽各位請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點公事需要去處理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想看一卷錄影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會再去看夜景好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們隨時都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在11點15分左右去接你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房間等就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麽錄影帶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他崇拜的一個冒險家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麽關口博之的紀錄片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又一次碰巧發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽冒險家的紀錄片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因爲他沈迷那種玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司才會被馬島那種人給搶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是什麽話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長不是你說的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤先生你怎麽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會爲馬島說話太陽打西邊出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你現在幫他說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無濟于事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是要你爲業績不佳負責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個月就要請你走路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過木山室內家飾的赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是母公司木山家具逼你制造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還把這股氣隨便遷怒在旁人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直嚷著“爲什麽叫我走路”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實大家都很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深怕你那樣有一天會把馬島給殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了沒有 橋本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須要告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司還有工作等著處理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是算了比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那張桌子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初看他是個好好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦咬住就會死纏不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是馬島一貫的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要跟他有任何牽扯比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們也早點回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就多坐一會 有什麽關系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊 明天會怎麽樣都很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喝的時候就要及時行樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這話說得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你不要喝了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麽晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生我看我們就喝到這裏結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 回房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一瓶酒沒喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生得意須盡歡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾到大家了真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還可以喝好幾杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把這個拿去 它治療宿醉很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什麽事我都在這
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時叫我一聲就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們早點睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走一直線嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喝成這樣都要怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該讓你爸爸喝這麽多酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就別放在心上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:17:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到哪裏都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝您幫我把他扶上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請早點休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你們久等了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千萬別這麽說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影帶好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支紀錄片真的非常有臨場感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這就要去遙望山那裏看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是毛利叔叔也來看看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常跟我爸一起來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸以前也很喜歡這裏的夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的夜景還好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個美景真是叫人感動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們喜歡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先去睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淩佳姐晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你帶我們去看夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你們這麽喜歡就值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你早點休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淩佳姐姐 你怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麽回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽事叫成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬島社長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 立刻去打電話報警
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麽事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能過去這是一起他殺案件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了保存現場完整
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不能到院子裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以爲你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下毛利小五郎 是一名偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位名偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長的遺體好像有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽地方不對勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的遺體周圍 竟然都沒有腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.17,0:22:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麽把社長放到那裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麽拖過的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果照叔叔的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體應該不會那樣橫躺在這裏才對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這麽一來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.61,0:24:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.46,0:24:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流石庭的玄機（後篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.61,0:24:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.13,0:24:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排水溝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是解決篇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.11,0:24:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸 犯人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒睡覺 還不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:17.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:27.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我倆討論的未來中必定有你我的歸屬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意成爲你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:42.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你我牽緊的手發誓與你共此一生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:49.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我討厭你”這句話即使是玩笑話我也不忍出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我喜歡你”這句話如果不是事實我也不會說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:05.07,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在無法見面時沒有心思顧及其他一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:10.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也被你一個人所獨占
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:24.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了不讓我倆的愛分隔兩地請你緊緊擁抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:31.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此心緒不甯的夜晚仍會造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:39.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時就請你給我一個大大的擁抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:27.29,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當清晨來臨我便會想起你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:33.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時只要在你身邊就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:39.88,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲恐懼時間的流逝黯然淚下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:45.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每出現在不斷改變的人心之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:58.79,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抱期待就不會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:05.64,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也別因此無欲無求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:13.01,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論前方是什麽樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:20.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夢醒之後你的人依然在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:25.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我的心意先一步飄向你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:33.14,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落英缤紛的這條路依舊沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:38.92,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然想挽著你的手漫步其中
